reviews.review_text:
hot show I helped to circulate this, so maybe I'm biased, but this is a very nice tape of a really hot show.  Big-time energy from Memphis Blues through pre-drums.  

I so love these Memphis Blues renditions with Jerry screaming the background vocals and raging on the solo!

Pretty great ChinaRider, with a really playful intro.

30 years ago, last night.
